{"tid":1048884,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"各位考完牌 用咗幾耐/有無買dream car","createTime":"2019-03-06T01:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T12:34:17.000Z","uid":162259,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0d52b4ffab414a866526c828c93f575f8aa18ea6","tid":1048884,"uid":162259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱考完 2take 第一次考肥泊車<br />\n90後 由細睇頭D大<br />\n雖然每次都係86最尾抽頭贏<br />\n但係心水清應該都知 R32先係車皇<br />\n所以由細到大 喺街見親部30年咸豐錢七 都會勁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾年唔知係咪我哋呢批90後開始買得起車<br />\n啲R32由本身10幾 去到依家正常都2字尾<br />\nV SPEC嗰啲直情四十幾五十<br />\nR33 R34重貴<br />\n<br />\n本身份人唔特別鍾意飛 學車都畀師傅屌手車慢<br />\n只係由細到大都好鍾意車 對R32好有情意結 好想收藏一架<br />\n<br />\n所以想問吓各位巴打 由考牌到買到dream car 用咗幾耐<br />\n畀個目標自己都好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/095147_8693dd25c6338953d3ccd1e18f87b3b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F095147_8693dd25c6338953d3ccd1e18f87b3b3.png&h=9ee899a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e12bcbf2deedd636dcd9241bdb8828e686e7ec0","tid":1048884,"uid":46942,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"一考完即買"},{"pid":"77a5f712fb2db546c91ac825ad3663fadce7ee23","tid":1048884,"uid":162259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e12bcbf2deedd636dcd9241bdb8828e686e7ec0","tid":1048884,"uid":46942,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"一考完即買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"咩車"},{"pid":"949293802621a1fb6d79cad7f5d6518cd3bf818b","tid":1048884,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"點知你搵幾多同有幾多父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想要R32咪買部普通R32 GT-S頂住癮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fec9ff912fe112d2a21bd4c147